snippet.title: The Coma 2B: Catacomb | Release Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The Coma 2B: Catacomb will be available on October 25th!

The Coma 2B: Catacomb is a Korean survival horror adventure. It is the back story to the previous game, The Coma 2: Vicious Sisters, and a story bridge for the full series.

Wishlist it now:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1781890/The_Coma_2B_Catacomb/
